<li id="cite_note-25"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-25">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFToohey2007" class="citation book cs1">Toohey, Kristine (2007). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=ywy9aslk3M8C&amp;pg=PA100"><i>The Olympic Games: A Social Science Perspective</i></a>. CABI. p.&#160;100. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-84593-355-5" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-84593-355-5"><bdi>978-1-84593-355-5</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Olympic+Games%3A+A+Social+Science+Perspective&amp;rft.pages=100&amp;rft.pub=CABI&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-84593-355-5&amp;rft.aulast=Toohey&amp;rft.aufirst=Kristine&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3Dywy9aslk3M8C%26pg%3DPA100&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOperation+Cyclone" class="Z3988"></span></span>
